==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sight-seeing
<hw>Sight"-see`ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Engaged in, or
given to, seeing sights; eager for novelties or curiosities.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sight-seeing</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Sight-seeing
<hw>Sight"-see`ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of seeing sights;
eagerness for novelties or curiosities.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sight-seer</ent>⟦br⟧
